com.samsung.android.service.health.tracking.data

Class TrackerUserProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.samsung.android.service.health.tracking.data.TrackerUserProfile

  • public final class TrackerUserProfile
extends Object
    This class represents the user's profile, including height, weight, gender, and age data.

       TrackerUserProfile profile = new TrackerUserProfile.Builder()
                     .setHeight(height)
                     .setWeight(weight)
                     .setGender(gender)
                     .setAge(age)
                     .build();

    Since:
    1.0.0
    See Also:
    HealthTrackerService.getHealthTracker(HealthTrackerType, TrackerUserProfile)
